unions

public static BooleanGridList unions(BooleanGridList a,
                                     BooleanGridList b)
Return a list of unions between the entries in a and b. Only pairs with the same extruder are unioned. If an element of a has no corresponding element in b, or vice versa, then those elements are returned unmodified in the result.

Parameters:
a -
b -
Returns:

intersections

public static BooleanGridList intersections(BooleanGridList a,
                                            BooleanGridList b)
Return a list of intersections between the entries in a and b. Only pairs with the same extruder are intersected. If an element of a has no corresponding element in b, or vice versa, then no entry is returned for them.

Parameters:
a -
b -
Returns:

differences

public static BooleanGridList differences(BooleanGridList a,
                                          BooleanGridList b)
Return a list of differences between the entries in a and b. Only pairs with the same attribute are intersected. If an element of a has no corresponding element in b, then an entry equal to a is returned for that.

Parameters:
a -
b -
